      <text>9.3.5 (Expand binomial - (2x+3)^4 type)</text>
    </name>
    <questiontext format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>Expand the following binomial using the binomial formula: \( {@p@} \).&nbsp;</p><p>[[input:ans1]] [[validation:ans1]]</p>]]></text>
    </questiontext>
    <generalfeedback format="html">
      <text><![CDATA[<p>The binomial theorem states that \[ (a+b)^n = \sum_{r=0}^n \binom{n}{r} a^{n-r}b^{r} \] We can use this with \(n={@n@}\), \(a={@t1@}\) and \(b={@t2@}\).&nbsp;]]></text>
    </generalfeedback>
